;; Natural language goals and PDDL goals


        (define (domain movie-dom)
            (:predicates
        (movie-rewound)
        (counter-at-two-hours)
        (counter-at-zero)
        (have-chips)
        (have-dip)
        (have-pop)
        (have-cheese)
        (have-crackers)
    )
            (:types
        chips dip pop cheese crackers - object
        chips5 chips4 chips3 chips2 chips1 - chips
        dip5 dip4 dip3 dip2 dip1 - dip
        pop5 pop4 pop3 pop2 pop1 - pop
        cheese5 cheese4 cheese3 cheese2 cheese1 - cheese
        crackers5 crackers4 crackers3 crackers2 crackers1 - crackers)
                    

;; Goal: 
rewind the movie and eat chips with dip, cheese and crakers, and a soda

;; PDDL Goal: 
(:goal
        (and (movie-rewound)
            (counter-at-zero)
            (have-chips)
            (have-dip)
            (have-pop)
            (have-cheese)
            (have-crackers))
    )

<END>

        (define (domain Depot)
            (:predicates
        (at ?x - locatable ?y - place)
        (on ?x - crate ?y - surface)
        (in ?x - crate ?y - truck)
        (lifting ?x - hoist ?y - crate)
        (available ?x - hoist)
        (clear ?x - surface)
    )
            (:types
        place locatable - object
        depot distributor - place
        truck hoist surface - locatable
        pallet crate - surface
        depot0 - Depot
        distributor0 distributor1 - Distributor
        truck0 truck1 - Truck
        pallet0 pallet1 pallet2 - Pallet
        crate0 crate1 - Crate
        hoist0 hoist1 hoist2 - Hoist)
                    

;; Goal: 
place the first crate on the third pallet and the second crate on the second pallet

;; PDDL Goal: 
(:goal
        (and
            (on crate0 pallet2)
            (on crate1 pallet1)
        )
    )

<END>

        (define (domain travel)
            (:predicates
        (road ?from ?to)
        (at ?thing ?place)
        (driving ?p ?v)
        (bridge ?from ?to)
        (mobile ?thing)
        (person ?p)
        (vehicle ?v)

            (:types
        a b c d e f g jack bulldozer)
                    

;; Goal: 
the bulldozer is at location g and the jack is at location a

    )
